section.section:
The following are grounds for an immediate suspension of a license issued under this title:
Knowingly making a false statement in an application;
Three convictions for violations occurring on separate days within any 3-year period of provisions under this title;
Failure to submit a report required under this title or by regulation; or
Failure of a nonresident of the State to appear in court in accordance with a citation issued by a Natural Resources police officer, or to any other process issued by any court of Maryland, for violation of this title.
